Title: FSNCleaner
Description:
FSN Cleaner makes it easier to translate the game Fate/stay night.

You'll no longer have to handle the script or word-wrap yourself, nor to use some obscur command-line to repack the game files, this software will do everything for you, and if it doesn't, just ast and it will be soon :)

It's developed in C#/XAML/REGEX.
